# 8. DOMAIN MANAGEMENT

Each tenant owns its own domain.

Examples

findmyinterior.com

truedial.in

futuremarketplace.com

Each domain points to the SAME Laravel Backend.

Nginx routes incoming traffic.

Tenant Resolver loads corresponding tenant.

No duplicate deployments.

One deployment.

Many domains.

